messages.text: Where r u?? Y u actin weird??
he jus wanted 2 talk… over beers!!
and he bought them 4 me!! 4got how nice of a guy he can b!!
R u sure this is safe??
Me so I can keep track of how safe u r..
sayin how much he missed me
Ur letting him handle ur drinks??
I’m coming downtown jus 2 keep an eye out..
Y do u have her phone??
Would you like to wish her any goodbyes?
Would you like to say anything to her?
Y r u askin me this?? wat r u doin??
So now I’m going to hurt her..
I’m going to hurt her like she hurt me.
Wat r u doin with her u bastard?!
Is that what you want to tell her before the end?
How much she needs my help to walk. To operate. How ironic.
She could’ve lived. She could’ve lived with me forever.
I’m just paying back what was done to me..
i know the bar u were at!!
I didn’t want to end two lives today.
But hurting her and her best friend may be just what I need.
its dark… come out u coward..
I’ve called the police u bastard!!
Why did you have to go do that?
I guess they’ll join the game too..
I didn’t expect all of these people to be dragged into it… But that’s the way fate will have it.
Should’ve just said bye when you had the chance.
